ich makes every batch unique. I happily leave the shop granola on the shelves now, as this version seems like a healthier alternative (tastes much less sweet).</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-191886"><a id="comment-191886"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">cookingslave</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 6th May, 2013</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">I made this, it was a complete hit with my son who is a professional athlete, but went on to adapt it by turning it in to a flap jack with chocolate on top for my younger children.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-32246"><a id="comment-32246"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">shirls1</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 10th May, 2009</div> </header><div class="comment__ratin